{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1683-03_348", "resp": "nbb"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigal]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mars 1683 [tome 3], p. 348-349"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le lendemain de ce Mariage, une des meilleures Amies de la Mariée, ne pouvant luy rendre visite à cause d’une indisposition qui la retenoit au Lit, luy fit connoistre par ce Madrigal, la part qu’elle prenoit à sa joye."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Lors que l’Hymen par de sacrez liens"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous unit à l’Epoux que vostre cœur desire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne partage point les tendres entretiens"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "  Qu’un amour content vous inspire."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous ne songez qu’à ces plaisirs charmans"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Que cause en vostre cœur une si belle chaîne ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Et moy, malade au Lit, belle & jeune Climene,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Pour prendre part à vos contentemens,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "  Je suis insensible à ma peine."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce Madrigal fut fort approuvé d’une belle & nombreuse Compagnie, à qui la Mariée le fit voir. Il est de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " Diéreville, dont vous avez déja veu de fort jolis Vers, & par qui la Dame malade l’avoit fait faire."}]}]}